{"article_id":"Qmd4STIKHU4Z6bC3","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"My eyes are now wide open","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"and now realize","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"I ' ve been used","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"to spread messages","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"I don ' t believe in .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"I am distancing myself from politics","depth":4},{"id":6,"text":"and completely focusing on being creative ! ! !","depth":4},{"id":7,"text":"Kanye West has apparently had enough with politics ,","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"explaining in a series of tweets on Tuesday","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"that his eyes `` are now wide open .","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"'' I introduced Candace to the person","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"who made the logo","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"and they didn ' t want their name on it","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"so she used mine .","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"I never wanted any association with Blexit .","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"I have nothing","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"to do with it .","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"More specifically , West shut down recent accusations","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"that he designed the shirts for Candace Owens ' Blexit campaign ,","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"which seeks to convince black voters to exit the Democratic Party .","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"Over the weekend , she was quoted by Page 6","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"as gushing about West 's involvement .","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"\" Blexit is a renaissance","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"and I am blessed to say","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"that this logo , these colors , were created by my dear friend and fellow superhero Kanye West , \"","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"she reportedly said .","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"But on Monday , Owens released a statement","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"supporting West 's claim ,","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"saying ,","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"`` BLEXIT is a project","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"that is mine entirely . ''","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"And then on Wednesday , she posted a blog","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"calling `` rumors '' of her past statements `` a lie","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"that seems to have made its way around the world . ''","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"\" Kanye was completely right","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"to feel used in that regard","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"and","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"as I have done personally ,","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"I would like to publicly apologize to him for any undue stress or pain","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"the effort","depth":14},{"id":40,"text":"to correct","depth":15},{"id":41,"text":"that rumor has caused him , his business relationships , or his family , \"","depth":15},{"id":42,"text":"she wrote .","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"\" He simply never designed them . \"","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"West has been a lightning rod for controversy ,","depth":3},{"id":45,"text":"but that bled into politics with his embrace of Donald Trump and the `` Make America Great Again '' campaign .","depth":3},{"id":46,"text":"Two years after meeting with Trump","depth":5},{"id":47,"text":"when he was president-elect ,","depth":5},{"id":48,"text":"West went to the Oval Office","depth":5},{"id":49,"text":"to meet again the now-president .","depth":5},{"id":50,"text":"But what started as a sit-down","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"to discuss prison reform , manufacturing , and gang violence","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"devolved into the two men showering each other with compliments .","depth":5},{"id":53,"text":"West even referred to the MAGA hat","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"Trump gave him","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"as `` a Superman cape . ''","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":111,"left":99,"right":110,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":62,"right":98,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":62,"left":60,"right":61,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":60,"left":0,"right"